    <!-- TUTORIAL -->
    <string name="tutorial_scenario">
    &lt;h1&gt;Creating a scenario&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;1. Give name to your scenario (name must be unique)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;2. Press the \"&create_scene;\" button to add scenes to your scenario&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;3. When scenario is ready press the \"&add;\" button&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;&export_file;&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;You can export your created scenario as a json file by pressing the \"&export_file;\" button and by selecting
        where to export your scenario.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;&import_file;&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;It is also possible to import json scenario files in to your
        app, just press the \"&import_file;\" button and select the file to import.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;Deleting scenes&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;If you want to delete created scenes, just hold the created scene button and a confirmation
        popup will show up.&lt;/p&gt;</string>
    <string name="tutorial_scene">
    &lt;h1&gt;Creating a scene&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;1. Select your desired image for the scene&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;2. Give name to your scene (name must be unique)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;3. Write a question to your scene&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;4. Create at least one answer to your scene by clicking the \"&create_answer;\" button&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;5. When the scene is ready press the \"&done;\" button&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;Deleting an answer&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;If you want to delete created answers, just hold the created answer button and a confirmation
        popup will show up.&lt;/p&gt;</string>
    <string name="tutorial_answer">
    &lt;h1&gt;Creating an answer&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;1. Select a color to your answer&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;2. Write an answer&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;3. Select to what scene does this answer lead to&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;4. When the answer is ready press the \"&done;\" button&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Meaning of colors: Green is the desired answer, yellow is almost right and red is not so good
        answer.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;Note:&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;If you delete or rename scenes and some of the answers led to that scene, remember to
        go and change where those answers lead to.&lt;/p&gt;</string>
